## Dataset Attribution

This project uses the UCI Parkinson's Disease dataset:
Little, M.A., McSharry, P.E., Roberts, S.J., Costello, D.A.E., Moroz, I.M. (2007).
Exploiting Nonlinear Recurrence and Fractal Scaling Properties for Voice Disorder Detection.
BioMedical Engineering OnLine, 6(23). https://doi.org/10.1186/1475-925X-6-23

The dataset is freely available from the UCI Machine Learning Repository under an open license.

## Medical Disclaimer

This software is a **research and educational demonstration only**. It is **not a
diagnostic device** and must **not** be used to make clinical decisions. Consult a
qualified neurologist for any medical concern.
